==政治用途==
从20世纪70年代开始，加兹登旗就与[[自由意志主义|自由意志主义]]紧密相连。从2009年开始，它也与美国[[茶党运动|茶党运动]]联系在一起<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.newsweek.com/chris-pratt-gadsden-flag-twitter-reacts-1449792 |title=Why Was Chris Pratt Wearing A Gadsden Flag? 'Avengers' Star Gets Conservative Support After T-Shirt Sparks Controversy |publisher=Newsweek |date=2019-07-17 |accessdate=2019-07-28 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815003633/https://www.newsweek.com/chris-pratt-gadsden-flag-twitter-reacts-1449792 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wtnh.com/dpp/news/hartford_cty/gadsden-flag-denied-over-state-capitol |title=Gadsden flag denied over State Capitol |publisher=Wtnh.com Hartford CT |date=May 26, 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101213150159/http://www.wtnh.com/dpp/news/hartford_cty/gadsden-flag-denied-over-state-capitol |archivedate=2010-12-13 |accessdate=2016-08-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aipnews.com/talk/forums/thread-view.asp?tid=14555&posts=3 |title=Gadsden Flag Now Officially "Offensive" In America |publisher=Aipnews.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717200926/http://www.aipnews.com/talk/forums/thread-view.asp?tid=14555&posts=3 |archivedate=2011-07-17 |accessdate=2016-08-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/ideas/articles/2010/06/13/flag_daze/ |title=Flag daze |work=Boston Globe |date=2010-06-13 |first=Tom |last=Scocca |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304230412/http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/ideas/articles/2010/06/13/flag_daze/ |archivedate=2016-03-04 |accessdate=2016-08-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由于这些多重用途，加兹登旗的含义不明确，取决于具体背景<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/the-shifting-symbolism-of-the-gadsden-flag |title=The Shifting Symbolism of the Gadsden Flag |publisher=The New Yorker |date=2016-10-02 |accessdate=2019-07-17 |archive-date=2020-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121104300/https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/the-shifting-symbolism-of-the-gadsden-flag |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/453488-conservatives-defend-chris-pratt-for-wearing-dont-tread-on-me |title=Conservatives defend Chris Pratt for wearing 'Don't Tread On Me' t-shirt |publisher=The Hill |date=2019-07-17 |accessdate=2019-07-17 |archive-date=2019-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717173308/https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/453488-conservatives-defend-chris-pratt-for-wearing-dont-tread-on-me |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.snopes.com/fact-check/president-obama-is-banning-the-dont-tread-on-me-flag/ |title=President Obama Is Banning the ‘Don’t Tread on Me’ Flag? |publisher=Snopes |date=2016-08-05 |accessdate=2019-07-17 |archive-date=2022-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220530091616/https://www.snopes.com/fact-check/president-obama-is-banning-the-dont-tread-on-me-flag/ }}</ref>。

